            "title": "A new early Miocene bat (Chiroptera: Phyllostomidae) from Panama confirms middle Cenozoic chiropteran dispersal between the Americas",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Gary S.",
                    "lastName": "Morgan"
                },
