            "title": "A new species of nectar-feeding bat, genus Lonchophylla, from the Caatinga of Brazil (Chiroptera, Phyllostomidae)",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Ricardo",
                    "lastName": "Moratelli"
                },
