            "title": "Reassessment of the evolutionary relationships within the dog-faced bats, genus Cynomops (Chiroptera: Molossidae)",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Ligiane M.",
                    "lastName": "Moras"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
